00:44:09,390 --> 00:44:11,310
all the hopping parameters are the same

1017
00:44:11,310 --> 00:44:14,220
so that you really have this
fully delocalized system,

1018
00:44:14,220 --> 00:44:15,480
like you expect.

1019
00:44:15,480 --> 00:44:17,190
So if you do this parameterization,

1020
00:44:17,190 --> 00:44:20,280
you can solve for the eigenvalue
spectrum of the system.

